				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12366640#post-4343348</guid>
				<title>Galaxy Brain +1</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12366640/scp-4247#post-4343348</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2019 02:16:53 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>SoullessSingularity</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>637830</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>In my headcanon bob was an IRL person with a real magical device that lets him transfer into fiction, and he was fleeing into fiction from something big and spooky. And that fiction he fled into was the SCP Foundation, and of course, in order to flee into the Foundation he must be written into it. Being written into it as someone with a magical ability means being contained. Thus, this fictionalized document is a testament to a real life person fleeing the real world into a fictional space and fitting into the universe seamlessly.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
